race.comment: THINKHARDANDFAST (16) is an honest commodity who has only missed a drum once in ten career starts. Will be at peak fitness for this and gets the services of Jones to handle the sticky draw. Should be right there when the whips are cracking. MARGOT'S DEEL (13) grows a leg for hoop Graham who has two wins and two placings from just four rides. Hard to knock mares in form and looms as the main danger. DIVAKARA (9) goes well here on his home circuit not missing a quinella spot in seven outings. Has to be included in calculations. CONTILDA'S LOVE (20) is a two-time winner here who rarely puts in a poor one. One for the exotics players. BIG TICKET BOY (17) rounds out the selections in a very open affair.
